      "span_text": "Niemistö et al. [CITATION_1] (rated as level B quality) investigated the effects of combined MT2 (myotensive lumbopelvic mobilization techniques) with exercises (stabilizing exercise to correct lumbo-pelvic rhythm) and UMC in comparison to UMC alone (patient education, stay active approach, ergonomic instruction, home general exercises, and educational-booklet) in patients with chronic LBP from QTF 1-3.",
